OL,3,CResidents call for long term solution
OL,4,Cto ferry issues
OL,6,FWindermere residents who claim they
OL,7,Fare being 'cut off' from local
OL,8,Fservices say a long-term solution is
OL,9,Fneeded to keep their car ferry in
OL,10,Foperation.
OL,12,FMallard, which is run by Westmorland
OL,13,Fand Furness Council, carries vehicles
OL,14,Fand passengers across England's
OL,15,Flargest lake between Bowness and Far
OL,16,FSawrey.
OL,18,FIn November 2024, the ferry was taken
OL,19,Fout of action because it needed a new
OL,20,Fengine and was shut again earlier this
OL,21,Fyear for three weeks.
