OL,3,CResidents call for long term solution
OL,4,Cto ferry issues
OL,6,F"If I have a hospital appointment at
OL,7,FKendal and I'm aiming for a particular
OL,8,Ftime, then I can miss it, if I depend
OL,9,Fon the ferry.
OL,11,F"The information system isn't right
OL,12,Fbecause the signs say the ferry isn't
OL,13,Fworking, but it is working, or you
OL,14,Farrive having passed several signs,
OL,15,F'ferry is working', but it's not
OL,16,Fworking. It's really frustrating."
