OL,3,CResidents call for long term solution
OL,4,Cto ferry issues
OL,6,F"We feel that keeping this one going
OL,7,Fis actually more reliable. It's part
OL,8,Fof the Westmorland and Furness highway
OL,9,Fsystem. And we are obliged to keep the
OL,10,Fhighway open. So at the moment, we
OL,11,Fdon't have the choice to cease the
OL,12,Fferry, even if we wanted to - which we
OL,13,Fdon't.
OL,15,F"We are totally committed to keeping
OL,16,Fthis ferry running. We've just put a
OL,17,Fnew engine in, for example, new drive
OL,18,Fsystems, new gearboxes. So a lot of
OL,19,Fthe mechanicals are fairly new. And
OL,20,Fmost of the interruptions in service
OL,21,Fare actually due to weather."
