OL,3,CResidents call for long term solution
OL,4,Cto ferry issues
OL,6,FBusiness owner Claire McKeever, says
OL,7,Fshe 'heavily relies' on the ferry
OL,8,Fservice to run Pure Lakes Skin Care.
OL,10,FShe said: "Quite a lot of our staff
OL,11,Fuse it every day. And in our
OL,12,Fcustomers, we've noticed a drop in
OL,13,Fpeople just popping in. We run classes
OL,14,Fevery week and people have been
OL,15,Farriving much more stressed or late
OL,16,Fbecause they're having to drive
OL,17,Faround. So that's having far reaching
OL,18,Frepercussions.
