OL,3,CResidents call for long term solution
OL,4,Cto ferry issues
OL,6,F"The ferry is a literal lifeline for
OL,7,Fall of us who live on this side of the
OL,8,Flake because the ambulances and the
OL,9,Ffire services use it. So we do really
OL,10,Ffeel cut off when it isn't running.
OL,11,FAnd it's a wonderful service when it
OL,12,Fworks well and we really, really need
OL,13,Fit to continue."
